  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The authors of ISO 26262 are aware that no safety standard is fully applicable to the development of software tools,&#xD;
    instead the assessment must ensure that an adequate and relevant subset of requirements from the safety standard are&#xD;
    selected.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The assessment method itself should also follow a national or international standard such as CMMI, SPICE or ISO 15504.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To ensure the&amp;nbsp;process used to develop the SW tool is in compliance with a safety standard.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
